data.description: Beautiful 2-story home with 4-sided brick and a 2-car garage! Hardwood floors in the kitchen and eat-in area!  The kitchen area also features a pantry, breakfast bar and an entertainment/message center nook with additional storage. The home features a guest bedroom and full bathroom on the main level. Owners suite is exceptionally large with a sitting area and private bath with walk-in closet, double vanity, separate shower and a large welcoming jetted tub. Staircase boasts  beautiful wrought-iron spindles and wide upstairs hallway is an added bonus! Solar panels are installed and included w/the purchase. They generate roughly 60% of the needed yearly electricity. The backup battery, when fully charged, will allow all house functions to run for approx. 8 hrs, with both air conditioning units running. Outside storage cabinet has space for addt'l back up solar batteries to be added, potentially tripling the back up capacity. Welcome home.
